instructions: Put the dinner plate on the place mat.
Put the salad plate on the dinner plate.
Put the napkin on the salad plate.
Put the wine glass on the upper right side of the place mat.
Put the water glass next to and a little behind the wine glass.
Put the salad fork on the left side to the dinner plate.
Put the dinner fork between the salad fork and the dinner plate on the place mat..
Put the dinner knife on the right side of the dinner plate.
Put the soup spoon on the right side of the dinner knife.
